533
00:53:12,000 --> 00:53:18,000
Unit Economics Placeholder.
echo "=== UNIT ECONOMICS ===" then cost per RAG query TBD, cost per API call TBD.

534
00:53:18,000 --> 00:53:24,000
Now view your complete baseline document.
cat tilde slash finops-baseline.txt

